In order to run commands with access to installed Python packages and CUDA, you need to use a Nix
virtual environment and possibly uv.
Run all commands with: nix run /home/enolan/mystuff/code/pip-shell-flake -- $COMMAND
Run commands that need Python stuff with: nix run /home/enolan/mystuff/code/pip-shell-flake -- uv run $COMMAND